thread.title: Rocio Rmz
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Rocio Rmz

author: Rocio Rmz
title: Rocio Rmz
text: This store has great customer service and everything is well organised despite the huge crowds it attracts. It does take time to try on your dress but it can be worth it! It also has a good variety of styles and all accessories for XV and prom dresses. If you have time and patience to wait in line, this is the store for you!
